<li id="cite_note-18"><b><a href="#cite_ref-18" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.ecoresults.org/success_tiptons.html" class="external free" title="http://www.ecoresults.org/success_tiptons.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.ecoresults.org/success_tiptons.html</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-19"><b><a href="#cite_ref-19" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.iisd.ca/ymb/sdrea/html/ymbvol149num1e.html" class="external text" title="http://www.iisd.ca/ymb/sdrea/html/ymbvol149num1e.html" rel="nofollow">IISD RS summary of the International Conference on Renewable Energy in Africa - 16-18 April 2008 - Dakar, Senegal</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-20"><b><a href="#cite_ref-20" title="">^</a></b> FAO&#160;: <a href="http://www.fao.org/docrep/010/a1598e/a1598e06.htm" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.fao.org/docrep/010/a1598e/a1598e06.htm" rel="nofollow">[1]</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-21"><b><a href="#cite_ref-21" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.claverton-energy.com/download/138/" class="external text" title="http://www.claverton-energy.com/download/138/" rel="nofollow">ADRECS - Aerially Delivered Reforestation and Erosion Control</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-22"><b><a href="#cite_ref-22" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.claverton-energy.com/download/54/" class="external text" title="http://www.claverton-energy.com/download/54/" rel="nofollow">The Sahara Project a new source of freshwater food and energy</a></li>
